{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_05_01",
  "title": "サニーピース 05 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……あれと、それからこれも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… That one‚ and then this one too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.1071654319999995,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4127.6736714,
          "startTime": 4.9276736714
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みんな、お疲れさん。……おや？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ everyone. …Oh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3204987844,
      "endTime": 10.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくらは真剣な顔で何をしているんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ what are you doing with such a serious face?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9333333333,
      "endTime": 14.316031583200001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4600,
          "startTime": 15.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "新たに思いついたやりたいことを\n『やってみたかったリスト』に書き込んでいるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's writing down new things she wants to do\nin her \"Things I Wanted to Try List.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.529365031,
      "endTime": 19.909364954700003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そういえばさくらは、やりたいと思ったことを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ Sakura used to note down",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1093650501,
      "endTime": 23.633333333299998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "書き留めてリストにしているんだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "everything she wanted to do in a list.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6333333333,
      "endTime": 26.3646258037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "アイドルになっていろんなことが実現したから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that she's an idol and achieved so much‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5712924322,
      "endTime": 29.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "やりたいこともかなり減ったと思うが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought the list would have shrunk quite a bit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8,
      "endTime": 32.624376138100004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "それが、数が減るどころか\nやりたいことは日々増えているみたいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ far from decreasing‚\nthe things she wants to do seem to grow every day…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8243762335,
      "endTime": 38.620861466799994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "やりたいことが無限にわいてくるなんて\nさくららしいですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wanting to do infinite things\nis so like Sakura‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8075281144,
      "endTime": 43.657528305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "欲張りなのは悪いことじゃないさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being greedy isn't a bad thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8708615621,
      "endTime": 47.03333333330001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "夢があるから人は頑張れるし、人生は楽しいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Dreams give people strength‚ and they make life fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0333333333,
      "endTime": 51.3597052892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。やりたいことが一杯あるさくらちゃんは\nいつも笑顔で、毎日楽しそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right. Sakura-chan‚ with all her goals‚\nis always smiling and looks so happy every day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5463721276,
      "endTime": 59.4263720514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "これでよし、と……\nわっ！　三枝さん！？　いつからそこにいたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There‚ that should do it…\nWah! Saegusa-san!? Since when were you there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6330386799,
      "endTime": 66.507936446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さっきからいたぞ。俺の存在にも気付かないくらい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been here for a while. You were so absorbed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7146028837,
      "endTime": 71.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "リストを書くのに夢中だったみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "in your list that you didn't even notice me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9666666667,
      "endTime": 74.9202492079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……なあ、さくらはどういうきっかけで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Say‚ Sakura‚ what made you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.1135822933,
      "endTime": 78.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そのリストを書き始めたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "start writing that list in the first place?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8333333333,
      "endTime": 80.9235825221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "この『やってみたかったリスト』は\n大切な友達から教えてもらったんです――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I learned about this \"Things I Wanted to Try List\"\nfrom a very precious friend of mine――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1102491697,
      "endTime": 86.3702506384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.5202520689
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.5202520689
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.7702520689
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "（小さい頃の私は体が弱くて、目眩を起こしたり）\n（熱を出して寝込むことがよくあった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（When I was little‚ I was frail and often felt dizzy）\n（or ended up in bed with a fever.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5702520689,
      "endTime": 96.8367370924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "（そういう時、お母さんがいつもそばにいてくれて……）\n（お母さんの笑顔を見ると、私は安心出来たんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Whenever that happened‚ Mom was always by my side…）\n（Seeing her smile made me feel safe.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1300686519,
      "endTime": 106.57678095509999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.916778787
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "（小学校に入る前、お母さんは体の弱い私を心配して）\n（大きな病院に連れて行って検査を受けさせた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Before I started grade school‚ Mom was worried about my health）\n（and took me to a large hospital for tests.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.916778787,
      "endTime": 116.47900107699999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "（そこで重い心臓の病気だと診断されて、幼かった私は）\n（「そうだったんだ」くらいしか思わなかったけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I was diagnosed with a severe heart condition‚ but back then‚）\n（I only thought‚ \"Oh‚ I see‚\" but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.8323319435,
      "endTime": 125.5158015251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "（お母さんは凄くショックを受けて……いつも笑顔の）\n（お母さんが、その日は部屋で一人で泣いてたんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mom was devastated… That day‚ even though she always smiled‚）\n（she was crying all alone in her room.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8358069102,
      "endTime": 135.848753802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.0554203351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura's",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくら……ごめんね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura… I'm so sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0554203351,
      "endTime": 141.2333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura's",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私が健康な体に産んであげられなかったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because I couldn't give you a healthy body…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2333333332,
      "endTime": 145.0062362988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura's",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくらは何も悪くないのに……辛い思いさせて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You did nothing wrong… but I'm making you suffer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.2195697466,
      "endTime": 151.8333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura's",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ごめんね……ごめんね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry… I'm so sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.8333333332,
      "endTime": 155.3707946459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.6707853952
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "（どうしてお母さんが謝るのか分からないけど）\n（私のせいで泣いてるってことはなんとなく理解出来た）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I didn't understand why Mom was apologizing‚）\n（but I could somehow sense she was crying because of me.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6707853952,
      "endTime": 164.7897198358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "（どうしたら、お母さんを幸せに出来るんだろう……）\n（どうしたら、ずっと笑顔でいてくれるんだろう……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（What can I do to make Mom happy?…）\n（How can I keep her smiling?…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.1030437468,
      "endTime": 173.2754473685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.6087786673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "（私は一生懸命考えて……）\n（お母さんの前では笑っていようって思った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I thought about it with all my might…）\n（and decided that I would always smile in front of her.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.6087786673,
