    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "女の子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Girl",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-tomo005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、無理しなくていいんだよ。もっと素直に\n笑いたい時は笑って、泣きたい時は泣いていいんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you don't have to push yourself. You can be more honest.\nSmile when you want to smile‚ and cry when you want to cry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 421.0145369846,
      "endTime": 429.94788068120005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
