      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_01-tomo006.m4a",
      "text": "うん、いいよ～。泣き顔を見られるのが嫌だったら……\nほら、おいで。私がぎゅーってしてあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's fine~. And if you don't want anyone to see you crying…\nHere‚ come here. I'll give you a big hug.",
        "id": ""
